import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { PropsTable, Playground } from 'docz';
import LoginComponent from './LoginComponent.tsx'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"logincomponent"}}>{`LoginComponent`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}>{`Basic Usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<LoginComponent authenticateWithGoogle={event => event.preventDefault()} />`} __scope={{props,LoginComponent}} >
  <LoginComponent
    authenticateWithGoogle={(event) => event.preventDefault()}
  />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="hr" components={components}></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={LoginComponent} /></MDXTag>
